  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The armiger may add a +1 competence bonus to CMD and saves against all maneuvers and effects that targets her active weapon. This bonus increase by +1 at class level 5 and every 5 class levels thereafter. Additionally, she may ignore the broken condition on her customized weapons. This ability does not allow the armiger to benefit from any abilities that allow her to give the broken condition to a weapon to trigger them unless she chooses to suffer the normal penalties of the broken condition on that weapon until it is repaired.</p>\n",
